  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100025602\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2de31d9e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UGPWNQxzb8cqqE16uFl3vAbTXxrT6JdIDiaucsau3vkpDuEXdHF4PVE49WY1wQWocribiaeKxXMkcNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AI寒武纪\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ICgnAptln0Xg6w3lVHUFXrtY5Tia7rfUDkTmCwe5Gz5RRAtVR2CX6UgcZiaFWnxksH1fkSSmjxichSCic8CTGqcElA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"一起见证人工智能的寒武纪大爆发，传播一切有关AI的技术\" data-id=\"Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 1.5em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM领域，线性注意力机制正在回归，工程实践主要还是国产模型在推进，主要原因大家都清楚，我们算力有限，当然也有长期的目标，Agent要真正落地干活，注意力机制必须要改变，目前国外主要模型都是闭源的，技术细节我们不了解，看起来都是仗着有卡，暴力解算，以下是这场技术路线之争的简要梳理</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 8px;margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16.5px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(183, 110, 121);line-height:1.2;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px 0px 0px 3px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">早期：效率与精度的两难</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">线性注意力并非新技术。早在2020年代，相关论文就已大量涌现。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">其核心目标是将注意力机制的时间和内存复杂度从O(n²)降低到O(n)，从而在处理长序列时实现更高的效率。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，这些早期的尝试从未真正获得主流认可。根本原因在于，它们以牺牲模型精度为代价，因此从未被应用在任何一个开源的、达到业界顶尖水平（SOTA）的大语言模型中。</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 8px;margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16.5px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(183, 110, 121);line-height:1.2;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px 0px 0px 3px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">新的浪潮：国产模型引领</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">转折点发生在今年下半年，线性注意力变体迎来了一轮复兴</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">6月，MiniMax-M1</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：拥有4560亿总参数、460亿激活参数的MoE模型，采用了“闪电注意力”（lightning attention）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">8月，Qwen3-Next</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：由Qwen3团队推出，采用了线性注意力变体</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">9月，DeepSeek V3.2</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：由DeepSeek团队发布，采用了稀疏注意力（sparse attention），虽然并非严格的线性，但仍是亚二次方复杂度</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这三个模型的共同点是，在大部分或所有层中，都用高效的线性或亚二次方注意力变体取代了传统的二次方注意力</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 8px;margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16.5px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(183, 110, 121);line-height:1.2;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px 0px 0px 3px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">剧情反转：MiniMax悄然“倒戈”</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">就在线性注意力看似前景大好之时，剧情出现了反转。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax团队发布了其新的2300亿参数模型M2，但出人意料地放弃了线性注意力，回归了常规注意力机制</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">团队给出的解释是，线性注意力在生产环境的LLM中非常棘手。虽然它在处理常规提示时表现尚可，但在推理和多轮对话任务中存在明显的精度问题——而这两项能力对于聊天会话和智能体应用至关重要</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一举动一度让外界认为，线性注意力的探索或许不值得再继续下去</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 8px;margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16.5px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(183, 110, 121);line-height:1.2;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px 0px 0px 3px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi入局：混合策略带来新解法</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，上周，Kimi团队发布了其全新的</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi Linear</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">模型，再次将线性注意力拉回舞台中央。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方数据显示，与常规的全注意力（full attention）相比，Kimi Linear实现了：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">75%的KV缓存缩减</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">最高达6倍的解码吞吐量</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在架构上，Kimi Linear与Qwen3-Next有诸多相似之处，两者都依赖于一种混合注意力策略。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来说，它们都将轻量级的线性注意力与重量级的全注意力层结合使用。两者的比例均为</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">3:1</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，即每三个采用线性注意力（Gated DeltaNet变体）的Transformer块，就搭配一个使用全注意力的块</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但Kimi Linear在此基础上进行了改进：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">线性部分</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：采用了Kimi Delta Attention (KDA)机制，这是对Gated DeltaNet的精炼，关于KDA解读可以看我之前的文章<a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&amp;mid=2247509242&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9ff5b32c9e432623ed6081ac0ff41289&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"刚刚！Kimi Linear横空出世，全新注意力架构：1M长文本解码速度飙升6.3倍，KV缓存砍掉75%\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">刚刚！Kimi Linear横空出世，全新注意力架构：1M长文本解码速度飙升6.3倍，KV缓存砍掉75%</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline-color: oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);\"><span leaf=\"\">全注意力部分</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：用多头潜在注意力（multi-head latent attention, MLA）取代了标准的全注意力模块</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然Kimi Linear的论文中没有与Qwen3-Next的直接比较，但与Gated DeltaNet论文中的Gated DeltaNet-H1模型（本质上是Gated DeltaNet与滑动窗口注意力的结合）相比，Kimi Linear在保持相同token生成速度的同时，实现了更高的建模精度</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">需要的注意的目前Kimi Linear中的多头潜在注意力（MLA）尚未整合输出门（sigmoid bypass），但团队计划在未来加入这一特性</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;outline-color:oklab(0.144521 0.000007 0.000003 / 0.5);text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度分析了线性注意力机制在 LLM 领域的回归与挑战，重点介绍了国产模型（MiniMax、Qwen、DeepSeek）的探索，以及 Kimi Linear 通过混合策略解决精度问题的创新。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度分析了线性注意力机制在 LLM 领域的回归与挑战，重点介绍了国产模型（MiniMax、Qwen、DeepSeek）的探索，以及 Kimi Linear 通过混合策略解决精度问题的创新。",
  "summary": "文章详细梳理了线性注意力机制在大型语言模型（LLM）中的发展历程和当前趋势。早期线性注意力因牺牲模型精度而未能普及，但近期国产模型如 MiniMax-M1、Qwen3-Next 和 DeepSeek V3.2 再次将其引入，旨在解决算力限制下的效率问题。然而，MiniMax-M2 模型又悄然回归传统注意力机制，指出线性注意力在推理和多轮对话中存在精度问题。Kimi 团队随后发布 Kimi Linear 模型，采用混合注意力策略（3:1 的线性注意力与全注意力结合），并引入 Kimi Delta Attention (KDA)和多头潜在注意力（MLA）进行改进。Kimi Linear 在实现 75% KV 缓存缩减和最高 6 倍解码吞吐量的同时，保持了更高的建模精度，为兼顾效率与精度的 LLM 架构提供了新的解决方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "线性注意力机制旨在提升 LLM 效率，但早期尝试因精度问题未能普及。",
      "explanation": "线性注意力通过将复杂度从 O(n²)降至 O(n)来提高长序列处理效率，但历史上常以牺牲模型精度为代价，未被主流 SOTA 模型采用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "国产模型正积极探索线性注意力，以应对算力限制，但面临生产环境的精度挑战。",
      "explanation": "MiniMax、Qwen、DeepSeek 等国产模型尝试引入线性或亚二次方注意力，但 MiniMax-M2 的回归表明其在推理和多轮对话中仍有精度短板。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Kimi Linear 采用混合注意力策略，有效平衡了 LLM 的效率与精度。",
      "explanation": "Kimi Linear 通过 3:1 的线性与全注意力结合，并引入 KDA 和 MLA，实现了 KV 缓存大幅缩减和解码吞吐量提升，同时保持了高精度，为长文本处理提供可行方案。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "LLM 领域，线性注意力机制正在回归，工程实践主要还是国产模型在推进，主要原因大家都清楚，我们算力有限。",
    "根本原因在于，它们以牺牲模型精度为代价，因此从未被应用在任何一个开源的、达到业界顶尖水平（SOTA）的大语言模型中。",
    "团队给出的解释是，线性注意力在生产环境的 LLM 中非常棘手。虽然它在处理常规提示时表现尚可，但在推理和多轮对话任务中存在明显的精度问题。",
    "与常规的全注意力（full attention）相比，Kimi Linear 实现了：75%的 KV 缓存缩减，最高达 6 倍的解码吞吐量。",
    "具体来说，它们都将轻量级的线性注意力与重量级的全注意力层结合使用。两者的比例均为 3:1。"
  ],
